2. the japanese is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person watching thriller movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic       | thriller |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | 7up    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

